  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to demonstrate the safety and effectiveness of the Adacolumn
      Apheresis System to treat the signs and symptoms of ulcerative colitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study Type: Interventional Study Design: Treatment, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo
      Control, Parallel Assignment, Safety/Efficacy Study.
